# Privacy Policy for Mazady (مزادي)

**Last updated:** February 27, 2026

## Privacy Policy — English

This Privacy Policy applies to the mobile application "Mazady" (مزادي) (package name: com.east4serv.moaffers), developed and published by East for Services (the “Developer”, “we”, “us”, or “our”).

### 1. Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following information:
- **Personal information you provide:** name, email address, phone number, and other account information provided during registration.
- **Location data:** current location data (GPS) to provide location-based services, such as showing nearby advertisements or allowing you to set the location of your own ads.
- **Ad data:** images, descriptions, and categories of items you post for sale or auction.
- **Activity and usage data:** search history, interaction with ads, timestamps, app configuration, and other analytics data.
- **Log data:** IP address, device model, OS version, crash logs and other diagnostic information collected automatically.

### 2. Permissions
The app may request permissions to:
- **Location:** to provide location-aware features and maps.
- **Camera:** to capture images of products when you create an advertisement.
- **Storage/Photos:** to upload images from your gallery to your advertisements.
- **Notifications:** to send alerts for messages, ad updates, and account activities.

### 3. Third-Party Services
We use third-party services that may collect or process certain data on their own terms. These include but are not limited to:
- **Google Play Services** — [https://policies.google.com/privacy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
- **Firebase Analytics & Crashlytics** — [https://firebase.google.com/policies/analytics](https://firebase.google.com/policies/analytics) and [https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)
- **Google Maps** — [https://www.google.com/help/terms_maps/](https://www.google.com/help/terms_maps/)

### 4. Use of Data
We use collected data to:
- Provide and maintain the platform for posting and viewing classified ads.
- Facilitate communication between buyers and sellers.
- Improve app functionality and user experience based on usage patterns.
- Diagnose and fix technical issues.
- Send important updates and notifications related to your ads and account.

### 5. Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell personal data. We may share data with:
- Service providers who perform services on our behalf (analytics, crash reporting, hosting).
- Law enforcement or other parties when required by law or to protect our rights.

### 6. Data Security
We use commercially reasonable measures to protect data. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.

### 7. Children
The app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

### 8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy. The “Last updated” date at the top will reflect the change.

### 9. Contact
